#   Binary Name:
#
#       Boot Manager (PC/AT)
#
#   Abstract:
#
#       This module implements the Boot Manager that can load a Minoca OS
#       loader. It is targeted for BIOS (non-UEFI) platforms.
#
#   Author:
#
#       Evan Green 21-Feb-2014
#
#   Environment:
#
#       Boot
#
